        {
            "type": "section",
            "title": "1. Simple Present Tense (सामान्य वर्तमान काल)",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "This tense is used for universal truths, habits, daily routines, and scientific facts.<br>सार्वभौमिक सत्य, सिद्धांत, कहावतें, दैनिक क्रियाएँ और आदतें दर्शाने के लिए इसका प्रयोग होता है."
                },
                {
                    "type": "table",
                    "content": {
                        "title": "वाक्य रचना (Structure)",
                        "headers": [
                            "प्रकार",
                            "सूत्र (Formula)",
                            "उदाहरण (Example)"
                        ],
                        "rows": [
                            [
                                "Positive (+)",
                                "Subject + V1 (s/es) + Object",
                                "He **plays** cricket. (वह क्रिकेट खेलता है।)"
                            ],
                            [
                                "Negative (-)",
                                "Subject + do/does + not + V1 + Object",
                                "He **does not play** cricket. (वह क्रिकेट नहीं खेलता है।)"
                            ],
                            [
                                "Question (?)",
                                "Do/Does + Subject + V1 + Object?",
                                "**Does** he **play** cricket? (क्या वह क्रिकेट खेलता है?)"
                            ]
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "type": "section",
                    "title": "Rules for 's' / 'es' (क्रिया के साथ नियम)",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "note",
                            "content": "ये प्रत्यय **केवल** तब लगते हैं जब कर्ता **Third Person Singular (He, She, It या एक नाम)** हो।"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "table",
                            "content": {
                                "title": "S/ES Rules",
                                "headers": [
                                    "Rule (नियम)",
                                    "Condition (शर्त)",
                                    "Example (उदाहरण)"
                                ],
                                "rows": [
                                    [
                                        "Add '-es'",
                                        "If verb ends in: **s, ss, sh, ch, x, o, z**",
                                        "go → go**es**, teach → teach**es**, pass → pass**es**, fix → fix**es**"
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "Add '-ies'",
                                        "If verb ends in **consonant + y** (व्यंजन + y)",
                                        "fly → fl**ies**, cry → cr**ies**, try → tr**ies**"
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "Add '-s'",
                                        "If verb ends in **vowel + y** (स्वर + y)",
                                        "play → play**s**, buy → buy**s**, say → say**s**"
                                    ],
                                    [
                                        "Add '-s'",
                                        "Other cases (बाकी सभी में)",
                                        "run → run**s**, eat → eat**s**, drink → drink**s**"
                                    ]
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
